Class MainMeal

java.lang.Object
logic.Item
logic.MainMeal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MainMeal extends Item implements Serializable
MainMeal represents a main meal item in the restaurant menu. This class extends the abstract Item class.
